sentEmails.subject: Inquiry About MEng Computer Science Program Intake and Application Availability
sentEmails.body:
Dear Carly MacLeod, I hope this message finds you well. My name is Manan Pathak, and I am
interested in applying for the Master of Engineering (MEng) program in
Computer Science at the University of Waterloo. I noticed on the program's
website that it offers start dates in spring, fall, and winter. However, I
was wondering if there are any available intakes earlier than the fall
session next year and if applications for those sessions are still open. I am highly motivated to begin the program as soon as possible, and I would
greatly appreciate any guidance or suggestions you can offer regarding this
matter. Thank you for your time and assistance. I look forward to your response. Best regards,
Manan Pathak
